title: 'Quality is not good'
body: 'Very thin fabric looks transparent I want to return it'

title: 'Beautiful kurti set if 5'
body: Soft, very very, comfy! The wide waist is truly as they advertise - it comfortably covers things, no muffin top problem. I'm also very happy that they truly fit, and are long enough.

title: 'Quality of leggins'
body: I'm received colorful leggins with super quality. Received as per product page image. Its have good Flexibility, length and adjustable. Cost also moderate compared to others.
